      <title>《读卖新闻》称野村因债券市场操纵面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据读卖新闻报道，日本金融监管机构计划建议对野村控股公司涉嫌操纵政府债券期货市场处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
